## üö® TROUBLESHOOTING

### If restore script fails:
1. Check if WSL is installed (needed for building)
2. Run script as Administrator
3. Use Option B (manual restore) instead

### If models aren't switching:
1. Check .env file has correct syntax (no extra quotes/spaces)
2. Restart Claude Desktop completely
3. Check logs in `%APPDATA%\Claude\logs\`

### If VibeCoder won't start:
1. Check Claude Desktop config points to correct paths
2. Verify build completed successfully
3. Try reverting to external config only (Option C)

